rase%20for%20all%20the%20power%20and%20all%20the%20positive%20things%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20potential%20negative%20things.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EChesnot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20no%20single%20definition%20for%20artificial%20general%20intelligence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDario%20Amodei%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Anthropic%2C%20previously%20predicted%20that%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20AI%26quot%3B%20could%20arrive%20by%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmodei%20said%20AGI%20is%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20has%20a%20different%20way%20of%20describing%20the%20next%20AI%20milestone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20is%20confident%20that%20we're%20rapidly%20approaching%20a%20new%20technology%20threshold%20%E2%80%94%20the%20creation%20of%20AI%20systems%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bbetter%26quot%3B%20than%20humans%20at%20most%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20just%20not%20willing%20to%20pin%20the%20buzzy%20term%20%26quot%3BAGI%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAGI%20has%20never%20been%20a%20well-defined%20term%2C%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said%20on%20a%20recent%20appearance%20on%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7LNyUbii0zw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESquawk%20Box%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20thought%20of%20it%20as%20a%20marketing%20term.%20But%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20way%20I%20think%20about%20it%20is%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20we're%20gonna%20get%20to%20AI%20systems%20that%20are%20better%20than%20almost%20all%20humans%20at%20almost%20all%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAGI%20is%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagi-predictions-sam-altman-dario-amodei-geoffrey-hinton-demis-hassabis-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20tech%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20many%20predicting%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20rapidly%20approaching%20viability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20there%20is%20no%20widely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreed-upon%20definition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20AGI%2C%20much%20less%20a%20concrete%20timeline%20for%20reaching%20it.%20However%2C%20in%20general%2C%20many%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20form%20of%20AI%20that%20can%20meet%20or%20exceed%20human%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Amodei's%20case%2C%20he%20said%20he%20prefers%20to%20think%20about%20future%20advanced%20AI%20systems%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20of%20geniuses%20in%20a%20data%20center.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sort%20of%20evocative%20phrase%20for%20all%20the%20power%20and%20all%20the%20positive%20things%2C%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20all%20of%20the%20potential%20negative%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20thing%20I%20think%20we're%20quite%20likely%20to%20get%20in%20the%20next%20two%20or%20three%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20has%20previously%20written%20an%20essay%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-anthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-defines-artificial-general-intelligence-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubject%20of%20AGI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20prefers%20to%20call%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20AI.%26quot%3B%20In%20it%2C%20he%20laid%20out%20a%20series%20of%20parameters%20for%20the%20technology%2C%20including%20being%20%26quot%3Bsmarter%20than%20a%20Nobel%20Prize%20winner%20across%20most%20relevant%20fields.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20same%20piece%2C%20he%20predicted%20it%20could%20arrive%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20AI%20field%2C%20Amodei%20said%20he's%20more%20confident%20than%20ever%20about%20such%20a%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout