%20positions%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%20he%20hired%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-professional-runner-vanessa-fraser-vc-firm-benchmark-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanessa%20Fraser%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20standout%20Stanford%20University%20athlete%20who%20inked%20a%20deal%20to%20run%20professionally%20for%20Nike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20has%20grounded%20me%20into%20a%20more%20disciplined%20routine%2C%20which%20translated%20to%20higher%20functioning%20and%20higher%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20previously%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20surprise%20to%20me%20is%20that%20I'm%20almost%20less%20tired%20than%20when%20I%20was%20a%20full-time%20professional%20athlete.%20I'm%20more%20mentally%20stimulated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3680d09-8eaa-4961-ad3f-1c4feb724c58%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVC%20firms%20are%20seeking%20out%20college%20athletes%20with%20transferable%20skills%20that%20could%20make%20them%20great%20investors.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investors%20like%20James%20Green%2C%20a%20background%20in%20sports%20has%20been%20a%20value-add%20for%20his%20VC%20firm%2C%20CRV.%20Growing%20up%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20many%20young%20people%20tapped%20by%20the%20British%20government%20as%20part%20of%20an%20elite-sports%20development%20initiative.%20He%20spent%2015%20years%20as%20a%20rower%2C%20culminating%20with%20a%20spot%20on%20Harvard%20University's%20rowing%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%2C%20who%20focuses%20on%20investing%20in%20cybersecurity%20and%20fintech%20startups%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20VC%20and%20rowing%20are%20similar%20because%20they're%20both%20team%20and%20individual%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20team%2C%20you%20can't%20win%2C%20but%20you're%20only%20as%20good%20as%20your%20slowest%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20the%20same%20in%20VC%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20all%20a%20team%2C%20individually%20making%20our%20own%20investments.%20When%20I%20make%20an%20investment%2C%20the%20team%20wins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20added%20that%20sports%20have%20also%20taught%20him%20patience.%20Training%20for%20years%20towards%20an%20athletic%20goal%20has%20parallels%20to%20a%20long%20career%20investing%20in%20startups%20and%20dealing%20with%20high%20and%20low%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rowed%20at%20a%20high%20level%20for%20years%2C%20which%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20doing%20sets%20on%20the%20rowing%20machine%20and%20working%20out%20multiple%20times%20per%20day%2C%20sometimes%20just%20to%20get%20one%20second%20faster%20or%20even%20plateau.%20It's%20the%20same%20when%20you're%20in%20the%20early%20stage%20for%20startups.%20You%20have%20to%20prepare%20for%20it%20to%20be%20nonlinear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapitalG%20vice%20president%20Kelly%20Barton%20also%20says%20that%20playing%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20in%20her%20past%20and%20present%20life%20%E2%80%94%20has%20made%20her%20a%20better%20investor.%20The%20former%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20rower%2C%20who%20joined%20CapitalG%20In%202021%2C%20transitioned%20to%20running%20marathons%20after%20graduating%20and%20later%20found%20success%20in%20the%20triathlon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20spoke%20to%20BI%20in%20mid-December%2C%20she%20was%20about%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Taup%C5%8D%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20IRONMAN%2070.3%20World%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20that%20I've%20appreciated%20is%20that%20workouts%20create%20a%20forced%20space%20for%20me%20to%20think%20about%20the%20companies%20I%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BStepping%20back%20for%20two-plus%20hours%20a%20day%20helps%20me%20find%20the%20space%20to%20think%20about%20their%20next%20steps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapitalG%20general%20partner%20Jesse%20Welder%20%E2%80%94%20who%20himself%20was%20on%20the%20University%20of%20California-Berkeley's%20sailing%20team%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI%20that%20Barton%20and%20the%20other%20members%20of%20his%20team%2C%20who%20all%20happen%20to%20be%20former%20college%20athletes%2C%20have%20extra%20drive.%20There%20are%20mulitple%20former%20student%20athletes%20at%20CapitalG%2C%20including%20AI%20investing%20partner%20Jill%20Chase%2C%20who%20was%20captain%20of%20Williams%20College's%20women's%20basketball%20team%2C%20and%20managing%20partner%20Laela%20Sturdy%2C%20who%20was%20captain%20of%20the%20women's%20basketball%20team%20at%20Harvard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAthletes%20are%20competitively%20driven%20people%20who%20are%20driven%20to%20succeed%20more%20than%20the%20average%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20an%20investing%20job%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20that%20you%20can%20keep%20learning%2C%20and%20it%20never%20stops%20mentally.%20Endurance%20athletes%2C%20and%20athletes%20in%20general%2C%20are%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarton's%20work%20at%20CapitalG%20has%20continued%20to%20complement%20her%20sport%3A%20she%20won%20her%20age%20group%20at%20December's%20IRONMAN%2070.3%20World%20Championships%20and%20became%20a%20world%20champion%20for%20women%20ages%2025-29.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20my%20best%20athlete%20when%20I'm%20my%20best%20self%2C%20and%20that%20means%20that%20I'm%20well-rested%2C%20and%20I'm%20devoting%20time%20to%20my%20relationships%20and%20my%20work%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fendurance-sports-college-athletics-are-shaping-the-future-of-vc-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737540001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ac5be10c98eace912f89d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22orig