ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuting-nyc-dc-helps-career-development-salary-millennial-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercommuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20defined%20by%20traveling%20more%20than%2075%20miles%20to%20work.%20The%20share%20of%20supercommutes%20in%20the%2010%20largest%20US%20cities%20was%2032%25%20greater%20between%20November%202023%20and%20February%202024%20than%20between%20the%20same%20time%20period%20four%20years%20prior%2C%20per%20a%20study%20from%20Stanford%20University%20that%20was%20published%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20this%20increase%20was%20likely%20driven%20by%20the%20uptick%20in%20remote%20working%20arrangements.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20Americans%20who%20moved%20away%20from%20their%20offices%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-americans-move-from-cities-rural-areas-millennials-gen-x-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20housing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20decided%20they%20could%20stomach%20a%20long%20commute%20when%20their%20employers%20rolled%20out%20return-to-office%20policies%20after%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235ae448a-d64c-49bf-8011-7d442b87bf4e%5C%22%3EDriving%20several%20hours%20is%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20job%20and%20pay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20said%20he%20earns%20between%20%2480%2C000%20and%20%24100%2C000%20annually%20from%20teaching%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20courses%20he%20teaches%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20student%20interest%2C%20among%20other%20factors.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGrant%20estimated%20that%20he%20dedicates%20about%2030%20hours%20a%20week%20to%20his%20teaching%20job%2C%20which%20includes%2012%20hours%20of%20lecturing%20and%20additional%20time%20spent%20in%20meetings%2C%20conducting%20office%20hours%2C%20preparing%20for%20classes%2C%20and%20grading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20said%20that%20his%20round-trip%20commuting%20costs%20typically%20include%20between%20%2440%20and%20%2450%20for%20a%20full%20tank%20of%20gas%2C%20roughly%20%2480%20for%20one%20night%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20about%20%2425%20in%20tolls%2C%20and%20%2436%20to%20park%20at%20the%20school%20%E2%80%94%20a%20total%20of%20about%20%24200%20per%20round-trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20committed%20to%20driving%20as%20his%20preferred%20mode%20of%20transportation%2C%20Grant%20said%20he%20tried%20taking%20the%20train%20and%20flying.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20the%20train%20can%20take%20up%20to%20six%20hours%20if%20there%20are%20delays%2C%20and%20that%20flying%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20also%20come%20with%20delays%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20doesn't%20save%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Grant%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20keep%20supercommuting%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20He%20said%20the%20biggest%20downside%20of%20the%20commute%20is%20that%20he%20has%20to%20be%20away%20from%20his%20wife%20two%20days%20a%20week.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20he%20enjoys%20teaching%20and%20that%20working%20with%20students%20helps%20him%20stay%20up%20to%20date%20on%20what's%20popular%20with%20younger%20wine%20and%20beer%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20also%20give%20him%20a%20leg%20up%20at%20his%20public%20relations%20job.%20He%20said%20he's%20considered%20looking%20for%20teaching%20jobs%20closer%20to%20home%2C%20but%20only%20a%20few%20schools%20offer%20similar%20courses.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20said%20the%20teaching%20job's%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20limited%20travel%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20are%20what's%20made%20his%20commute%20sustainable.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20he%20said%20the%20job%20could%20bring%20about%20another%20financial%20benefit%3A%20discounted%20college%20tuition%20for%20his%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinancially%20it%20still%20makes%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20commute.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20to%20say%20I%20would%20do%20it%20even%20if%20it%20wasn't%20but%20that's%20not%20realistic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20long%20commute%20to%20work%3F%20Are%20you%20willing%20to%20share%20your%20story%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-commuter-drives-long-distance-weekly-part-time-job-teacher-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737536822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67897c92ae09223df2ba5895%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-commuter-drives-long-distance-weekly-part-time-job-teacher-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waking%20up%20at%204%3A30%20a.m.%20and%20driving%20four%20hours%20one-way%20to%20a%20teaching%20job%20is%20worth%20it%20for%20Torrey%20Grant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-commuter-drives-long-distance-weekly-part-time-job-teacher-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20about%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20harder%20to%20buy%20knock-off%20Ozempic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ozempic%20behind%20red%20ropes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67893b4f8951662c9f20877f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3ENicolas%20Ortega%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20DeBenedetto%20has%20only%20been%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-really-like-find-affordable-weight-loss-drugs-patient-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompounded%20tirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20but%20she%20already%20feels%20like%20it's%20a%20life-changer.%20Her%20doctor%20prescribed%20the%20cheaper%2C%20generic%20version%20of%20the%20weight-loss%20drug%20after%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drug-insurance-coverage-access-employer-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurer%20refused%20to%20cover%20Zepbound%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20brand-name%20version%20made%20by%20Eli%20Lilly.%20DeBenedetto%2C%20now%2043%2C%20tells%20me%20she's%20been%20prediabetic%20since%20her%2020s%2C%20and%20after%20going%20through%20hormone%20injections%20with%20IVF%2C%20she's%20put%20on%20a%20worrying%20amount%20of%20weight%20she%20just%20can't%20take%20off.%20As%20we%20talk%2C%20she%20marvels%20that%20she's%20had%20a%20box%20of%20chocolates%20on%20her%20desk%20all%20day%20that%20she%20still%20hasn't%20touched%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20the%20result%20of%20both%20the%20drug%20and%20a%20psychological%20shift%2C%20since%20she%20hasn't%20been%20taking%20the%20injections%20that%20long.%20Still%2C%20the%20optimism%20is%20palpable.%20Those%20chocolates%20would%20%26quot%3Bnormally%20be%20gone%20in%20an%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeBenedetto's%20excitement%20has%20been%20stunted%2C%20however%2C%20by%20recent%20developments%20that%20will%20make%20compounded%20tirzepatide%20no%20longer%20widely%20available.%20The%20FDA%20has%20removed%20the%20drug%20from%20its%20shortage%20list%20and%20set%20a%20timeline%20for%20pharmacies%20to%20stop%20making%20compounded%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20only%20version%20available%20will%20be%20the%20FDA-approved%2C%20pricier%20type.%20She%20feels%20like%20the%20rug%20has%20been%20pulled%20out%20from%20under%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20devastated%20that%20this%20option%20is%20going%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20her%20doctor%20is%20going%20to%20switch%20her%20over%20to%20compounded%20semaglutide%20%E2%80%94%20the%20active%20pharmaceutical%20ingredient%20in%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20made%20by%20Novo%20Nordisk.%20The%20problem%20is%2C%20that's%20a%20temporary%20fix%2C%20too.%20While%20semaglutide%20is%20still%20on%20the%20shortage%20list%2C%20the%20FDA%20is%20expected%20to%20eventually%20end%20that%20designation%2C%20and%20compounders%20will%20have%20to%20stop%20making%20it%2C%20too.%20Lots%20of%20people%20could%20be%20in%20DeBenedetto's%20situation%3A%20The%20perfect%20candidate%20for%20a%20miracle%20drug%20whose%20miracle%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20easily%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1%20drugs%20such%20as%20semaglutide%20and%20tirzepatide%20are%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight-loss%20drug%20revolution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20biggest%20development%20in%20weight-loss%20medicine%20since%20bariatric%20surgery%20(not%20to%20mention%20less%20invasive)%2C%20the%20medications%2C%20which%20were%20initially%20approved%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20have%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20in%20recent%20years.%20People%20say%20the%20drugs%20help%20them%20drop%20pounds%20by%20cutting%20the%20%26quot%3Bfood%20noise%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20feel%20fuller%20longer%20and%20quieting%20their%20appetites.%20Recent%20research%20suggests%20these%20drugs%20could%20help%20treat%20a%20variety%20of%20other%20conditions%2C%20from%20sleep%20apnea%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-alcohol-addiction-alcoholism-treatment-weight-loss-drug-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavy%20drinking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drugs%20became%20so%20popular%20so%20fast%20that%20manufacturers%20began%20running%20out%2C%20and%20patients%20scrambled%20to%20find%20Ozempic%20or%20Wegovy%20(the%20brand-name%20versions%20of%20semaglutide)%20and%20Monjauro%20or%20Zepbound%20(tirzepatide).%20There%20were%20other%20barriers%20to%20access%3A%20The%20brand-name%20versions%20of%20the%20drugs%20are%20expensive%2C%20in%20most%20cases%20costing%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20without%20insurance%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-company-health-insurance-pay-weight-loss-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurers%20have%20been%20hesitant%20to%20cover%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20not%20everyone%20who%20wants%20to%20lose%20weight%20has%20a%20clinical%20need%20to%20%E2%80%94%20a%20doctor%20saying%20no%20to%20a%20prescription%20doesn't%20always%20quell%20the%20desire%20to%20get%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20access%20issues%20were%20alleviated%20when%20the%20FDA%20put%20the%20drugs%20on%20its%20shortage%20list%20in%202022.%20This%20allowed%20compounding%20pharmacies%20to%20get%20into%20the%20GLP-1%20game%20by%20creating%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20the%20injectible%20drugs%20using%20active%20ingredients%20obtained%20from%20chemical%20wholesalers%20and%20manufacturers%20that%20they%20could%20dispense%20when%20prescribed%20by%20a%20provider.%20Even%20though%20the%20FDA%20warned%20patients%20about%20the%20potential%20dangers%20of%20getting%20non-FDA-approved%2C%20compounded%20GLP-1s%2C%20the%20cat%20was%20out%20of%20the%20bag.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientist-cheaper-ozempic-sold-online-contains-dangerous-ingredients-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECompounding%20pharmacies%20and%20telehealth%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20saw%20an%20enormous%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20the%20demand%20for%20these%20copycat%20medications%20and%20offer%20them%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point.%20Eli%20Lilly%20and%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20obviously%2C%20didn't%20love%20the%20setup%2C%20but%20there%20wasn't%20much%20they%20could%20do%20to%20stop%20it%2C%20given%20the%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20about%20shortages%20is%20that%20they%20don't%20last%20forever.%20After%20some%20legal%20wrangling%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-shortage-of-weight-loss-drug-tirzepatide-zepbound-is-over-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%20pulled%20tirzepatide%20from%20its%20shortage%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%2C%20giving%20compounders%20a%20short%20grace%20period%20to%20wrap%20things%20up.%20That%20means%20people%20taking%20the%20copycats%20will%20soon%20need%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20name-brand%20version%2C%20find%20another%20drug%2C%20or%20stop%20taking%20anything%20altogether.%20The%20party%20is%20over%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20it's%20supposed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20knew%20when%20semaglutide%20went%20into%20shortage%20and%20then%20when%20tirzepatide%20went%20into%20shortage%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20permanent%20status.%20Eventually%2C%20those%20drugs%20would%20be%20available%20in%20quantities%20sufficient%20enough%20to%20meet%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Brunner%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Pharmacy%20Compounding%2C%20an%20industry%20group.%20Since%20October%2C%20when%20the%20FDA%20first%20determined%20the%20shortage%20was%20resolved%2C%20they've%20been%20warning%20members%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20end%20was%20near%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompounders%20aren't%20eager%20to%20pack%20it%20in.%20The%20Outsourcing%20Facilities%20Association%2C%20another%20industry%20group%20that%20represents%20compounders%20that%20produce%20large%20batches%20of%20medications%2C%20has%20sued%20to%20overturn%20the%20FDA's%20decision.%20Eli%20Lilly%20has%20since%20joined%20the%20FDA%20as%20a%20defendant%20to%20try%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20shortage%20stays%20resolved%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wants%20people%20taking%20and%20paying%20for%20its%20Monjauro%20and%20Zepbound%2C%20not%20cheaper%20copies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20an%20Eli%20Lilly%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20FDA%20has%20%26quot%3Bcorrectly%20determined%26quot%3B%20that%20tirzepatide%20is%20not%20in%20shortage%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bclear%20that%20compounders%20must%20immediately%20begin%20transitioning%20patients%20taking%20compounded%20tirzepatide%20knockoffs%20to%20FDA-approved%20tirzepatide%20medicines%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20will%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%20defend%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA's%20decision.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20best%20way%20to%20ensure%20patients%20get%20tirzepatide%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Bemployers%2C%20insurers%2C%20and%20the%20government%20to%20recognize%20that%20obesity%20is%20a%20chronic%20disease%20and%20to%20increase%20coverage%20of%20medicines%20to%20treat%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OFA%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%20The%20APC%20has%20not%20joined%20the%20suit%20in%20defense%20of%20the%20compounders%2C%20but%20Brunner%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20Eli%20Lilly's%20brief%20had%20gone%20too%20far%2C%20and%20if%20the%20court%20agrees%2C%20it%20could%20end%20compounding%20by%20smaller%20pharmacies%20of%20common%20drugs%2C%20such%20as%20lidocaine%20or%20amoxicillin%2C%20if%20they%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20fall%20into%20a%20shortage%20for%20one%20reason%20or%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20picture%20is%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20the%20line%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20GLP-1s%2C%20and%20the%20parties%20involved%20know%20it.%20Compounders%20have%20found%20a%20big%20revenue%20stream%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20easily%20give%20up.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%20and%20Novo%20Nordisk%20have%20market%20exclusivity%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20no%20generics%20are%20allowed%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20time%20and%20they%20want%20to%20make%20as%20much%20money%20as%20they%20can%20before%20it%20runs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%2C%20this%20all%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20confusion%2C%20changes%2C%20and%2C%20potentially%2C%20interruptions%20in%20treatment.%20The%20transition%20period%20will%20not%20be%20seamless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20very%20disappointed%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Melanie%20Jay%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20NYU%20Langone%20Comprehensive%20Program%20on%20Obesity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20providers%20have%20begun%20to%20switch%20patients%20from%20tirzepatide%20to%20semaglutide%20or%2C%20when%20they%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20to%20the%20brand-name%20drug.%20The%20telehealth%20company%20Ro%2C%20which%20in%20the%20past%20offered%20compounded%20tirzepatide%2C%20in%20December%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D5b5bcc09cf5c4715485052448727d6f043541180182526db7ac0e4c04543cf89%26postID%3D67857fac22e74339bb3c08a1%26postSlug%3Dfda-compounded-tirzepatide-semaglutide-shortage-ozempic-2025-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fro.co%252Fpress%252Fzepbound-single-dose-vials%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20be%20offering%20single-dose%20vials%20of%20Zepbound%20to%20patients%20with%20obesity.%20(It%20comes%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point%20than%20the%20medication%20when%20delivered%20in%20an%20injection%20pen.)%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20follow%20the%20FDA's%20guidance%20on%20compounding%2C%20and%20we'll%20work%20to%20ensure%20our%20patients%20have%20the%20best%20treatment%20options%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Ro%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20compounders%20and%20telehealth%20companies%20may%20try%20to%20find%20workarounds%20and%20loopholes%2C%20especially%20once%20semaglutide%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20shortage.%20John%20Hertig%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Butler%20University's%20College%20of%20Pharmacy%20and%20Health%20Sciences%2C%20explained%20that%20much%20of%20this%20depends%20on%20what's%20determined%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bessentially%26quot%3B%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20GLP-1%20in%20question%2C%20meaning%20it's%20too%20close%20to%20see%20it%20as%20anything%20other%20than%20a%20duplicate.%20Compounders%20can%20make%20patient-specific%20(and%20prescription-specific)%20versions%20of%20medications%20if%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20person%20is%20allergic%20to%20a%20dye%20in%20the%20FDA-approved%20version%20or%20has%20trouble%20swallowing%20something%20in%20pill%20form.%20But%20they're%20only%20allowed%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%20copies%20in%20very%20specific%20circumstances%20%E2%80%94%20say%2C%20a%20drug%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20space%20in%20this%20world%20where%20compounders%20are%20important%20when%20things%20go%20on%20shortage%20or%20if%20there's%20a%20supply%20chain%20issue%20or%20you%20need%20a%20patient-specific%20alteration%20of%20a%20medicine%20because%20of%20that%20patient's%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20Hertig%20said.%20The%20problem%2C%20he%20added%2C%20comes%20when%20compounders%20are%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20games%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bskirting%20that%20essential%20copy%20regulation%26quot%3B%20by%20adding%20a%20minor%20ingredient%20to%20make%20the%20drug%20technically%20different%20or%20changing%20its%20form%20of%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20becomes%20what%20counts%20as%20too%20close%20a%20copy%20to%20be%20allowed%20and%20whether%20a%20small%20alteration%20is%20really%20different%20%E2%80%94%20some%20entities%20might%20try%20to%20add%20vitamin%20B12%20to%20their%20drugs%20or%20deliver%20it%20in%20oral%20form%20and%20argue%20that%20it's%20OK.%20This%20could%20very%20well%20become%20battleground%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1s%20are%20a%20golden%20goose%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20give%20up%2C%20and%20investors%20know%20it.%20When%20the%20FDA%20took%20tirzepatide%20off%20of%20its%20shortage%20list%20in%20December%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhims-hers-falls-after-fda-ends-shortage-of-lilly-weight-loss-drug-1034157985%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20price%20of%20Hims%20%26amp%3B%20Hers%3C%2Fa%3E%20fell%20amid%20concerns%20about%20the%20telehealth%20company's%20GLP-1%20business.%20In%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fciti-downgrades-hims-hers-to-sell-on-valuation-concerns-1034214409%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECiti%20downgraded%20its%20rating%20on%20the%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20semaglutide%20would%20be%20off%20the%20shortage%20list%20within%20the%20next%20year.%20Hims%20%26amp%3B%20Hers%20has%20not%20offered%20compounded%20tirzepatide%20in%20the%20past%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20company%20said%2C%20but%20it%20does%20offer%20compounded%20semaglutide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20it's%20heard%20from%20patients%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20access%20branded%20GLP-1%20medications%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20over%20half%20of%20its%20customers%20couldn't%20access%20GLP-1s%20they%20were%20prescribed%20because%20of%20its%20price.%20They%20added%20that%20compounders%20serve%20a%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20purpose%26quot%3B%20and%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fdrugs%2Fhuman-drug-compounding%2Ffdc-act-provisions-apply-human-drug-compounding%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epart%20of%20the%20Federal%20Food%2C%20Drug%2C%20and%20Cosmetic%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bpermits%20the%20compounding%20of%20medications%20to%20address%20patients'%20clinical%20needs%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20a%20particular%20drug%20is%20subject%20to%20a%20shortage.%26quot%3B%20When%20I%20asked%20whether%20that%20meant%20they%20would%20keep%20compounding%20semaglutide%2C%20the%20response%20was%20vague.%20It%20indicated%20that%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20keep%20trying%20but%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20%26quot%3Bpersonalized%26quot%3B%20for%20patients%2C%20though%20it's%20unclear%20how%20they'll%20achieve%20that%20for%20thousands%20of%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20patients%20benefit%20from%20the%20standardized%20dose%20of%20GLP-1s%2C%20and%20right%20now%2C%20in%20this%20current%20shortage%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20unlocking%20access%20to%20these%20life-changing%20medications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20that%2C%20many%20patients%20can%20benefit%20from%20something%20different%20than%20the%20standardized%20dose%2C%20they%20need%20something%20more%20personalized%2C%20and%20this%20is%20an%20option%20that%20we%20make%20available%20on%20our%20platform%20and%20plan%20to%20do%20that%20for%20the%20long%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20FDA%20said%20the%20agency%20recommends%20patients%20use%20FDA-approved%20drugs%20when%20available%20and%20that%20compounded%20drugs%20should%20%26quot%3Bonly%20be%20used%20to%20fulfill%20the%20needs%20of%20patients%20whose%20medical%20needs%20cannot%20be%20met%20by%20an%20FDA-approved%20drug.%26quot%3B%20The%20agency%20also%20warned%20that%20compounded%20drugs%20pose%20a%20higher%20risk%20to%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20complicate%20things%2C%20the%20new%20presidential%20administration%20means%20new%20leadership%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20and%20the%20FDA%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20picked%20Ozempic-skeptic%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20to%20head%20the%20health%20department.%20In%20January%2C%20Hims%20%26amp%3B%20Hers%20donated%20%241%20million%20to%20Trump's%20inauguration%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20mess.%20The%20spigot%20is%20turning%20off%20for%20patients%20on%20compounded%20tirzepatide%2C%20and%20compounded%20semaglutide's%20days%20are%20numbered%2C%20too.%20Some%20providers%20will%20try%20to%20find%20workarounds%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20successful%20they'll%20be%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20successful%20regulators%20will%20be%20in%20stopping%20them.%20Patients%20can%20access%20the%20brand-name%20drugs%2C%20but%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20affordability%20remain%20problems.%20Once%20more%20reputable%20compounders%20leave%20the%20market%2C%20people%20might%20resort%20to%20sketchier%20operations%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20them%20to%20scammers%2C%20counterfeiters%2C%20and%20unsafe%20concoctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20this%20could%20also%20be%20a%20moment%20for%20a%20reset.%20It%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20healthcare%20industry%20taking%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20GLP-1%20access%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUp%20to%2070%25%20of%20people%20with%20obesity%20who%20start%20these%20meds%20are%20not%20on%20it%20at%20one%20year%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%20why%20people%20go%20off%20of%20it.%20Certainly%20insurance%20and%20costs%2C%20but%20also%20because%20I%20don't%20think%20people%20really%20know%20what%20they're%20getting%20into%20or%20don't%20have%20the%20support%20to%20really%20stay%20on%20them%2C%20or%20they%20think%20that%20somehow%20once%20they%20lose%20weight%2C%20they%20can%20go%20off%20of%20them%2C%20which%20is%20not%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20you're%20also%20looking%20at%2C%20how%20do%20we%20work%20with%20patient%20access%3F%26quot%3B%20Hertig%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20work%20with%20insurers%3F%20How%20do%20we%20manage%20the%20cost%20here%20where%20we're%20then%20incentivizing%20more%20patients%20to%20go%20to%20the%20manufacturer%2C%20which%20is%20FDA-approved%3F%20My%20hope%20would%20be%20that%20the%20manufacturers%20are%20also%20looking%20at%20that%20patient%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneric%20versions%20of%20Ozempic%20and%20Monjauro%20won't%20be%20available%20until%20their%20patents%20expire.%20What%20happens%20with%20compounding%20is%20unclear%2C%20but%20once%20these%20drugs%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20shortage%2C%20compounders%20are%20supposed%20to%20stop%20making%20them%2C%20except%20under%20very%20specific%20circumstances.%20Within%20that%20framework%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20thing%20is%20expensive%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20a%20valid%20reason%20for%20copying%2C%20as%20much%20as%20many%20patients%20wish%20that%20was%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20impossible%20to%20untangle%20exactly%20who's%20to%20blame%20here%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20any%20one%20party%20is%20at%20fault.%20It's%20the%20result%20of%20how%20the%20American%20health%20system%20is%20set%20up.%20Brand-name%20GLP-1s%20are%20much%20cheaper%20in%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20drugmakers%20could%20slash%20their%20prices%2C%20but%20the%20profit%20motive%20dictates%20that%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20to%2C%20they%20won't.%20Compounding%20pharmacies%20have%20been%20filling%20in%20a%20legitimate%20gap%2C%20though%20some%20have%20overstepped%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20quite%20easy%20to%20get%20GLP-1s%20from%20many%20providers%20without%20much%20of%20an%20examination.%20Both%20the%20big%20guys%20and%20little%20guys%20are%20pushing%20these%20drugs%20onto%20consumers%20through%20ads%20on%20television%20and%20online.%20Of%20course%2C%20people%20are%20clamoring%20for%20drugs%20that%20will%20improve%20their%20health%2C%20help%20them%20lose%20weight%2C%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereduce%20the%20stigma%20around%20their%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeBenedetto%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20government%20would%20take%20compounded%20tirzepatide%20away%20from%20her%2C%20even%20though%20the%20government%20is%20just%20doing%20what's%20outlined%20in%20the%20law.%20But%20like%20many%20other%20people%2C%20she%20didn't%20realize%20that.