%3F%20We%20can't%20shut%20out%20eyes%20to%20this%20fact...%20that%20you%20examined%20only%20four%20witnesses%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amanullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Amanullah%20pointed%20out%20the%20original%20chargesheet%20-%20which%20includes%20charges%20relating%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20an%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20officer%2C%20Ankit%20Sharma%20-%20had%20been%20filed%20in%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20this%20has%20to%20be%20looked%20at...%20you%20can't%20castigate%20somebody%20like%20this!%20He%20has%20not%20been%20out%20of%20jail%20even%20for%20a%20day%20in%20five%20years.%20I%20will%20have%20to%20write%20on%20this%20also%20(in%20my%20order).%20We%20can't%20shut%20our%20eyes%20(to%20this)....%20What%20is%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(on%20the%20right%20to%20personal%20liberty)%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Amanullah%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Hussain%20made%20a%20call%20to%20the%20Police%20Control%20Room%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20riots.%20%26quot%3B...%20not%20just%20that%20he%20made%20a%20call.%20Your%20(the%20police's)%20chargesheet%20records%20he%20sought%20help.%20Five%20years%20of%20these%20allegations...%20five%20years.%20How%20do%20you%20get%20over%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20examine%20your%20star%20witnesses%20for%205%20years!%20We%20refrain%20from%20commenting%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BUndertrial%20For%20Five%20Years%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Hussain's%20counsel%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Siddharth%20Aggarwal%2C%20had%20lamented%20the%20apparent%20lackadaisical%20efforts%20of%20the%20police%20in%20this%20matter.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20eye-witnesses%20turned%20hostile%20and%20the%20fifth%2C%20they%20(the%20police)%20say%20is%20not%20in%20Delhi%20and%20that%20they%20don't%20know%20when%20he%20will%20turn%20up...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20an%20undertrial%20for%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20prosecution%20had%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20rely%20on%2C%20a%20complaint%20under%20anti-terror%20law%20UAPA%20to%20continue%20to%20detain%20his%20client.%20%26quot%3BBut%20charges%20are%20not%20framed%20in%20that%20case...%20State%20has%20not%20completed%20its%20duty%20and%20am%20only%20asking%20for%2015%20days'%20bail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hussain's%20arguments%20also%20included%20references%20to%20bail%20for%20AAP%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20and%20then%20granted%20interim%20bail%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-gets-bail-will-be-released-from-jail-after-6-months-6554574%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Gets%20Bail%20After%206%20Months%2C%20Can't%20Go%20to%20Office%20Or%20Sign%20Files%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20reference%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20deputy%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20who%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20same%20case%20and%20was%20released%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20criticised%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanish-sisodia-has-right-to-speedy-trial-says-supreme-court-6297896%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTravesty%20Of%20Justice%26quot%3B%3A%20Sisodia%20Gets%20Bail%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Slams%20Delay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Manish%20Sisodia%20case%20court%20said%20that%20if%20there%20is%20delay%20in%20trial%20(and%20there%20is)%20long%20incarceration...%20even%20without%20getting%20into%20twin%20conditions%20(the%20thresholds%20for%20release)%20bail%20can%20