C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678fb0f1ae09223df2babc48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaci%20Rice%20in%20June%202023%20after%20her%20'mommy%20makeover'%20(left)%20and%20in%20November%202024.%3Cp%3EStaci%20Rice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20maintained%20her%20weight%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%20And%20although%20she%20started%20eating%20more%2C%20she%20presumed%20it%20wouldn't%20affect%20her%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-made-cravings-food-noise-in-my-head-disappear-semaglutide-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20noise%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20Rice's%20head%20%E2%80%94%20cravings%20for%20sugar%20and%20sweet%20treats%20when%20experiencing%20heightened%20emotions%20%E2%80%94%20gradually%20returned%2C%20and%20she%20regained%2026%20pounds%20over%20about%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20had%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20medication%20left%20which%20she%20would%20take%20now%20and%20then%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20and%20she%20couldn't%20afford%20her%20previous%20maintenance%20dose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20to%20notice%20my%20clothes%20were%20getting%20tighter%2C%26quot%3B%20Rice%20said.%20Knee%20problems%2C%20a%20swollen%20finger%2C%20and%20various%20other%20aches%20and%20pains%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadolsky%20said%20he'd%20seen%20clients%20who%20abruptly%20stopped%20taking%20GLP-1s%20because%20their%20insurance%20no%20longer%20covered%20them%20or%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-diabetes-drug-shortages-linked-to-tiktok-weight-loss-trend-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20regaining%20weight%20is%20the%20biggest%20risk%20associated%20with%20coming%20on%20and%20off%20the%20medicine%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObesity%20is%20a%20chronic%20disease%20and%20these%20medicines%20work%20by%20helping%20people%20manage%20their%20appetite%20and%20food%20noise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20these%20medicines%20must%20come%20down.%20And%20if%20insurance%20doesn't%20cover%20them%2C%20it%20would%20be%20ideal%20that%20the%20cost%20would%20be%20low%20enough%20to%20pay%20out-of-pocket%20for%20them.%20The%20medicines%20are%20not%20a%20short-term%20fix.%20They%20are%20designed%20and%20used%20for%20the%20chronic%20disease%20of%20obesity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELars%20Fruergaard%20J%C3%B8rgensen%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Novo%20Nordisk%20which%20makes%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20has%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F09%2F24%2Fozempic-wegovy-costs-congress-testimony%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20insurers%20and%20middlemen%20for%20the%20high%20prices%20of%20the%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299f68012-d2e9-48e2-9875-aa768e5ae138%5C%22%3EA%20side%20hustle%20to%20fund%20semaglutide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20Rice%20had%20started%20her%20side%20hustle%20and%20restarted%20the%20medication%20on%20a%20low%20dose%20to%20minimize%20costs%2C%20deciding%20when%20to%20start%20and%20stop%20without%20medical%20guidance.%20The%20cost%20was%20different%20depending%20on%20the%20provider%2C%20and%20she%20used%20the%20money%20from%20her%20%26quot%3Bvery%20stressful%26quot%3B%20jobs%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20takes%20a%20low%20weekly%20dose%20(0.25%20milligrams%20was%20her%20lowest%2C%20and%20her%20highest%202.5%20milligrams).%20A%2010-week%20supply%20costs%20her%20%24305%2C%20and%20she%20is%20budgeting%20to%20afford%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20get%20back%20on%20track%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20back%20to%20where%20I%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Rice%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20hate%20that%20I%20ended%20up%20spending%20a%20good%20amount%20on%20a%20mommy%20makeover.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20said%20she%20feels%20guilty%20that%20she%20put%20her%20family%20in%20a%20financial%20bind%20and%2C%20if%20she%20could%20go%20back%20in%20time%2C%20isn't%20sure%20she%20would%20have%20had%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20hopes%20she'll%20be%20back%20at%20her%20goal%20weight%20by%20February%2C%20and%20then%20plans%20to%20stay%20on%20a%20maintenance%20dose%20long-term.%20She%20sees%20regaining%20the%20weight%20as%20a%20valuable%20lesson%20that%20maintainance%20without%20medication%20isn't%20as%20easy%20as%20she%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20miracle%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Rice%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20always%20going%20to%20be%20an%20advocate%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-glp-1-weight-regain-woman-works-two-jobs-afford-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737533881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642acc98fb9f05001953d698%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-glp-1-weight-regain-woman-works-two-jobs-afford-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20who%20lost%2064%20pounds%20on%20a%20compounded%20form%20of%20the%20weight%20loss%20drug%20semaglutide%2C%20marketed%20as%20Wegovy%20and%20Ozempic%2C%20started%20a%20side%20hustle%20to%20afford%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemaglutide-glp-1-weight-regain-woman-works-two-jobs-afford-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFamily%20Planning%20Now%20Financial%20Decision%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Tax%20Jab%20At%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20class%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20tax%20terrorism%20and%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20government's%20ATM%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20today.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20whose%20outreach%20to%20middle%20class%20comes%20two%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20February%205%20election%20in%20Delhi%2C%20also%20listed%20seven%20Budget%20demands%20from%20the%20Centre%20that%20AAP%20MPs%20will%20raise%20in%20Parliament%20for%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20poll%20promises%20are%20made%20for%20the%20underprivileged%20classes%2C%20and%20some%20for%20a%20few%20industrialists.%20On%20the%20grounds%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%2C%20other%20parties%20have%20created%20a%20vote%20bank.%20And%20they%20need%20donations%20from%20industrialists%2C%20so%20they%20are%20the%20note%20bank.%20Between%20this%20vote%20bank%20and%20note%20bank%2C%20a%20large%20section%20is%20sandwiched.%20This%20is%20India's%20middle%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fq3c9GSbMLRY%3Fsi%3Df4UyTZTbzVtoumL7%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20successive%20governments%20after%20Independence%20have%20crushed%20and%20squeezed%20the%20middle%20class.%20%26quot%3BThe%20relationship%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20middle%20class%20is%20strange.%20They%20don't%20do%20anything%20for%20the%20middle%20class.%20But%20whenever%20the%20government%20needs%20to%2C%20they%20target%20the%20middle%20class%20through%20tax.%20Middle%20class%20pays%20huge%20taxes%2C%20but%20gets%20nothing%20in%20return.%20India's%20middle%20class%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20government's%20ATM.%20It%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20tax%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20class%2C%20he%20said%2C%20does%20not%20have%20very%20big%20demands.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20a%20good%20job%20or%20business%2C%20a%20house%20of%20their%20own%2C%20quality%20education%20for%20their%20children.%20They%20just%20want%20health%20and%20safety%20for%20their%20family.%20He%20only%20hopes%20for%20a%20little%20help%20from%20the%20government.%20But%20the%20government%20is%20making%20neither%20schools%20nor%20hospitals%2C%20it%20is%20not%20creating%20jobs%20and%20not%20ensuring%20safety%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20if%20all%20taxes%20are%20added%20up%2C%20a%20middle%20class%20person%20gives%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20income%20to%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20he%2Fshe%20dare%20to%20fulfill%20their%20dreams%20amid%20this%20tax%20terrorism%3F%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20for%20a%20young%20middle%20class%20couple%2C%20family%20planning%20has%20now%20become%20a%20financial%20decision.%20Before%20having%20a%20child%2C%20they%20ask%20themselves%20if%20they%20can%20afford%20the%20upbringing.%20Where%20have%20we%20reached%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20were%20leaving%20the%20country%20due%20to%20high%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20spends%20the%20people's%20money%20for%20their%20welfare.%20He%20underlined%20that%20Delhi%20government%20hiked%20the%20education%20budget%2C%20transformed%20state-run%20schools%20and%20also%20barred%20private%20schools%20from%20increasing%20fees.%20%26quot%3BWe%20lowered%20power%20and%20water%20bills%20to%20shield%20you%20from%20inflation.%20Delhi%20residents%20get%20the%20cheapest%20power%20among%20all%20major%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20AAP%20leader%20also%20showcased%20Delhi%20government's%20work%20in%20the%20healthcare%20sector%20and%20said%20the%20highest%20demand%20for%20mohalla%20clinics%20are%20in%20middle-class%20residential%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20appealed%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20identify%20middle%20class%20as%20the%20country's%20real%20superpower%20and%20provide%20them%20relief%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Budget.%20He%20said%20AAP%20MPs%20would%20raise%20middle%20class'%20issues%20in%20Parliament%20and%20listed%20seven%20demands.%20The%20demands%20include%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20education%20budget%2C%20a%20countrywide%20cap%20on%20private%20schools'%20fee%2C%20subsidy%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20a%20hike%20in%20health%20budget%20and%20tax%20removal%20from%20health%20insurance%20premiums%20and%20zero%20tax%20on%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20also%20demanded%20that%20GST%20be%20removed%20from%20essential%20commodities%2C%20robust%20retirement%20plans%2C%20free%20treatment%20and%2050%20per%20cent%20concession%20on%20train%20travel%20for%20senior%20citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20remarks%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20RP%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20he%20given%20to%20middle%20class%3F%20He%20promised%20free%20WiFi%2C%20where%20is%20it%3F%20he%20promised%20clean%20water%20for%20free.%20Where%20is%20water%20free%3F%20every%20household%20uses%20an%20RO%20machine.%20He%20had%20admitted%20he%20couldn't%20provide%20clean%20water.%20He%20is%20talking%20about%20education%2C%20every%20year%2C%20more%20than%201.5%20lakh%20students%20are%20made%20to%20drop%20out%20in%20Classes%209%20and%2011%20to%20improve%20their%20board%20results.%20What%20about%20their%20future%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20talking%20rubbish%20to%20fool%20people%2C%20but%20this%20won't%20work%20again%20and%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737533640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmc73sreg_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt