generation%20of%20advancements%20in%20AI%2C%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20include%20the%20construction%20of%20colossal%20data%20centres%2C%20very%20massive%20structures.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20business%2C%20these%20buildings%2C%20these%20are%20big%20beautiful%20buildings%20that%20are%20going%20to%20employ%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20and%20physical%20campuses%20in%20locations%20currently%20being%20scouted%20nationwide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20making%20their%20choices%20of%20locations.%20I%20think%20they%20have%20their%20choice.%20I'd%20like%20to%20ask%20Larry%2C%20Sam%20and%20Masa%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%20and%20just%20talk%20a%20little%20bit%20about%20what%20they're%20doing%20and%20if%20you%20have%20any%20questions%20and%20then%20we'll%20go%20into%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20subjects%20also.%20But%20this%20is%2C%20to%20me%2C%20a%20very%20big%20thing%2C%20a%20USD%20500%20billion%20Stargate%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEllison%20said%20they%20certainly%20couldn't%20do%20this%20without%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20simply%20be%20impossible.%20AI%20holds%20incredible%20promise%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20for%20every%20American.%20We've%20actually%20been%20working%20with%20Open%20AI%20for%20a%20while%20and%20with%20Masa%20for%20a%20while.%20The%20data%20centres%20are%20actually%20under%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20of%20them%20are%20under%20construction%20in%20Texas.%20Each%20building%20is%20half%20a%20million%20square%20feet.%20There%20are%2010%20buildings%20currently%20being%20built%2C%20but%20that%20will%20expand%20to%2020%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20beyond%20the%20Abilene%20location%2C%20which%20is%20our%20first%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20applications%20that%20we're%20building%2C%20to%20give%20you%20an%20idea%2C%20ma