OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20child%20will%20%26quot%3Bnever%26quot%3B%20be%20smarter%20than%20AI.%20The%20entrepreneur%2C%20on%20a%20recent%20podcast%20appearance%2C%20shared%20his%20vision%20of%20a%20future%20where%20artificial%20intelligence%20surpasses%20human%20intelligence.%20The%20soon-to-be-father%20believes%20this%20shift%20will%20be%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20life%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20kid%20is%20never%20gonna%20grow%20up%20being%20smarter%20than%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Altman%20remarked%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fsam-altman-on-the-future-of-ai-and-humanity%2Fid1554567118%3Fi%3D1000682967449%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERe%3A%20Thinking%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Adam%20Grant%2C%20saying%20such%20a%20reality%20would%20soon%20feel%20natural.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20it's%20smarter%20than%20us.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20can%20do%20things%20we%20can't%2C%20but%20also%20who%20really%20cares%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%2C%20preparing%20to%20welcome%20a%20child%20with%20his%20husband%20Oliver%20Mulherin%2C%20reflected%20on%20what%20skills%20his%20kid%20might%20need%20to%20thrive%20in%20an%20AI-driven%20world.%20He%20claims%20raw%20intelligence%20will%20take%20a%20backseat%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20kind%20of%20ability%20we%20still%20really%20value%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20raw%2C%20intellectual%20horsepower%20to%20the%20same%20degree.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20what%20mattered%20most%20was%20figuring%20out%20the%20right%20questions%20to%20ask%20over%20simply%20finding%20answers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prompting%20tricks%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20using%20in%202023%20are%20no%20longer%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Altman%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20way%20humans%20interact%20with%20AI%20will%20evolve%2C%20requiring%20deeper%2C%20more%20thoughtful%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPodcast%20host%20Adam%20Grant%20also%20offered%20his%20perspective%2C%20suggesting%20that%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bconnector%20of%20dots%26quot%3B%20will%20outweigh%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bcollector%20of%20facts%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20new%20era.%20Mr%20Altman%20agreed%2C%20recounting%20how%20resistance%20to%20tools%20like%20Google%20in%20schools%20ultimately%20gave%20way%20to%20more%20impactful%20ways%20of%20learning.%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20AI%20to%20be%20like%20that%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20on%20AI's%20evolution%20in%20chess%2C%20Mr%20Altman%20said%20that%20early%20models%20lost%20to%20humans%20but%20eventually%20beat%20them.%20However%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20best%20results%20come%20from%20teamwork.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20AI%20and%20humans%20working%20together%20in%20chess%20beat%20an%20AI%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman's%20vision%20for%20the%20future%20is%20one%20where%20AI%20revolutionises%20the%20economy%20and%20workforce%2C%20shifting%20the%20focus%20from%20raw%20intelligence%20to%20other%20human%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20I%20think%20the%20whole%20economy%20transforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20addressing%20concerns%20about%20job%20displacement.%20But%20he%20is%20optimistic%20about%20humanity's%20ability%20to%20adapt%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20always%20find%20new%20jobs%2C%20even%20though%20every%20time%20we%20stare%20at%20a%20new%20technology%2C%20we%20assume%20they're%20all%20going%20to%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Altman%20announced%20that%20OpenAI%20had%20finalised%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fopenai-finalizes-o3-mini-reasoning-ai-model-version-to-launch-it-soon-7499702%5C%22%3E'o3%20mini'%20reasoning%20AI%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20launch%20it