0wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRoughly%20half%20the%20exposed%20jobs%20may%20benefit%20from%20AI%20integration%2C%20enhancing%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Georgieva%20wrote%20in%20her%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20other%20half%2C%20AI%20applications%20may%20execute%20key%20tasks%20currently%20performed%20by%20humans%2C%20which%20could%20lower%20labor%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20lower%20wages%20and%20reduced%20hiring.%20In%20the%20most%20extreme%20cases%2C%20some%20of%20these%20jobs%20may%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737521998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67905ea5ae09223df2baea6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Altman%20said%20that%20a%20project%20like%20Stargate%20might%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20different%20president.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A147%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Safe%20Are%20India's%20Nuclear%20Reactors%3F%20What%20Global%20Watchdog%20Chief%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20nuclear%20reactors%20are%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20safe%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20applies%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20safety%20standards%20to%20its%20civil%20nuclear%20programme%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20global%20nuclear%20watchdog%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20(IAEA)%20has%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20Davos%202025%2C%20IAEA%20director%20general%20Rafael%20Mariano%20Grossi%20was%20asked%20how%20safe%20India's%20nuclear%20reactors%20are.%20''Absolutely%20safe.%20India%20applies%20to%20its%20civilian%20nuclear%20programme%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20internationally%20agreed%20and%20IAEA%20established%20nuclear%20safety%20standards%20and%20security%20guidance%2C''%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20fast-breeder%20nuclear%20reactor%20programme%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20is%20being%20developed%20at%20Kalpakkam%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Grossi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20an%20interesting%20add-on%20to%20its%20fleet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20imposed%20a%20voluntarily%20moratorium%20on%20nuclear%20explosive%20testing%20since%20the%20Pokhran%20tests%20in%201998.%20Asked%20if%20New%20Delhi%20would%20be%20within%20its%20rights%20to%20test%20if%20China%20or%20Pakistan%20went%20ahead%20with%20nuclear%20tests%2C%20Gross%20replied%2C%20''Our%20position%20and%20the%20position%20of%20the%20international%20community%20is%20that%20we%20should%20move%20to%20a%20general%20ban%20on%20nuclear%20testing%20so%20we%20hope%20that%20there%20won't%20be%20a%20need%20for%20further%20testing%2C%20neither%20in%20the%20subcontinent%20nor%20elsewhere.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20India%20should%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Nuclear%20Suppliers%20Group%2C%20which%20currently%20has%2048%20countries%20as%20its%20members%2C%20the%20IAEA%20chief%20said%2C%20''I%20have%20been%20President%20of%20the%20Nuclear%20Suppliers%20group%20and%20I%20interacted%20very%20actively%20in%20trying%20to%20bring%20this%20to%20an%20equitable%20solution%2C%20including%20with%20other%20countries%20which%20had%20similar%20aspirations.%20My%20interactions%2C%20even%20with%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20were%20extremely%20useful.%20We%20were%20very%20close%20at%20the%20time%20to%20a%20good%20outcome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there%20is%20a%20bigger%2C%20wider%20political%20scene%20which%20enters%20into%20the%20situation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20that.%20This%20is%20for%20the%20members%20to%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20India-US%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%20is%20set%20to%20achieve%20its%20full%20potential%20as%20Washington%20DC%20tries%20to%20negotiate%20the%20liability%20clause%20that%20will%20enable%20it%20to%20build%20reactors%20in%20India%2C%20Grossi%20said%20it%20was%20for%20India%20and%20US%20to%20decide.%20What%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20the%20Indian%20civil%20nuclear%20programme%20is%20among%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20diverse%20worldwide.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20every%20%5Bnuclear%5D%20technology%20and%20masters%20every%20technology%20in%20a%20very%20good%20way.%20I%20believe%20that%20with%20the%20current%20expansion%20and%20interest%20in%20nuclear%20energy%2C%20we%20are%20the%20best%20position%20to%20see%20those%20levels%20of%20cooperation%20and%20trade%20grow%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAEA%20chief%20also%20took%20questions%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20said%20there%20were%20several%20occasions%20when%20the%20watchdog%20feared%20a%20nuclear%20accident.%20%26quot%3BZaporizhzia%20is%20right%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20on%20the%20frontline%2C%20extremely%20fragile.%20It%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20shelling%2C%20and%20more%20frequently%2C%20blackouts.%20This%20means%20loss%20of%20cooling%20function%20might%20have%20led%20to%20a%20nuclear%20accident.%20We%20are%20counting%20it%20by%20the%20day%20when%20we%20have%20situations%20like%20this.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20that%20IAEA%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20West%20Asia%20situation%2C%20Grossi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20nuclear%20watchdog%20does%20not%20have%20any%20evidence%20that%20Iran%20is%20building%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%2C%20it%20has%20accumulated%20vast%20levels%20of%20enriched%20Uranium%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20close%26quot%3B%20to%20weapon-level%20grade.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20IAEA%20have%20not%20received%20Tehran's%20full%20cooperation%20in%20inspections%20and%20in%20clarifying%20its%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737521100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fh3qedsf8_ndtv-at-davos_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-at-davos-international-atomic-energy-agency-how-safe-are-indias-nuclear-reactors-what-global-watchdog-chief-replied-7530096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20nuclear%20reactors%20are%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20safe%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20applies%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20safety%20standards%20to%20its%20civil%20nuclear%20programme%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20global%20nuclear%20watchdog%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20(IAEA)%20has%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-at-davos-international-atomic-energy-agency-how-safe-are-indias-nuclear-reactors-what-global-watchdog-chief-replied-7530096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Panama%20lodges%20UN%20complaint%20over%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20threat%20to%20seize%20canal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737520803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117444165%2Cimgsize-1900533.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpanama-lodges-un-complaint-over-trumps-threat-to-seize-canal%2Farticleshow%2F117443749.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117443749.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPanama%20has%20raised%20concerns%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20over%20President%20Donald