944.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-administration-directs-federal-dei-staff-be-placed-on-paid-leave%2Famp_articleshow%2F117442944.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-administration-directs-federal-dei-staff-be-placed-on-paid-leave%2Famp_articleshow%2F117442944.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2222%20US%20States%20Sue%20Over%20Trump%20Bid%20To%20End%20Birthright%20Citizenship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20of%20Democratic-leaning%20states%20launched%20legal%20actions%20Tuesday%20seeking%20to%20block%20Donald%20Trump's%20plan%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20separate%20lawsuits%20involving%20a%20total%20of%2022%20states%2C%20including%20California%20and%20New%20York%2C%20come%20the%20day%20after%20Trump%20took%20office%20and%20quickly%20unveiled%20a%20phalanx%20of%20executive%20orders%20he%20hopes%20will%20reshape%20American%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20among%20them%20was%20an%20order%20eliminating%20the%20automatic%20granting%20of%20citizenship%20to%20anyone%20born%20on%20US%20soil%2C%20a%20right%20guaranteed%20by%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20of%20the%20country's%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20implemented%2C%20the%20order%20would%20prevent%20the%20federal%20government%20from%20issuing%20passports%2C%20citizenship%20certificates%20or%20other%20documents%20to%20children%20whose%20mothers%20are%20in%20the%20country%20illegally%20or%20temporarily%2C%20and%20whose%20father%20is%20not%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20permanent%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20President's%20executive%20order%20attempting%20to%20rescind%20birthright%20citizenship%20is%20blatantly%20unconstitutional%20and%20quite%20frankly%2C%20un-American%2C%26quot%3B%20California%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20as%20h