ral%20government%20employees%20say%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20return-to-office%20mandate%20won't%20make%20the%20government%20more%20efficient%20%E2%80%94%20and%20could%20have%20some%20unintended%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERandy%20Erwin%2C%20national%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Federal%20Employees%2C%20or%20NFFE%2C%20and%C2%A0Everett%20Kelley%2C%20national%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Government%20Employees%2C%20or%20AFGE%2C%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-orders-federal-workers-return-to-office-rto-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERTO%20mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20make%20the%20government%20less%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20score%20political%20points%20by%20insinuating%20that%20people%20on%20telework%20aren't%20coming%20to%20work%20when%20nothing%20could%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Erwin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20for%20telework%20and%20other%20family-friendly%20work%20methods%2C%20the%20federal%20government%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20be%20able%20to%20recruit%20and%20retain%20the%20talent%20that%20it%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Erwin%20said.%20The%20NFFE%20is%20the%20oldest%20union%20in%20the%20US%20and%20represents%20more%20than%20110%2C000%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-asks-for-list-of-federal-workers-to-fire-doge-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20can't%20make%20anywhere%20near%20what%20you%20could%20be%20making%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20some%20family%2C%20flexible%20work%20policies%20become%20a%20very%2C%20very%20important%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20current%20federal%20workers%20may%20also%20choose%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelley%2C%20who%20leads%20AFGE%2C%20the%20largest%20federal%20employee%20union%20representing%20800%2C000%20members%2C%20also%20said%20telework%20was%20important%20to%20attracting%20and%20retaining%20top%20talent%20within%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-targets-dei-mandates-federal-employees-day-one-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProviding%20eligible%20employees%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20hybrid%20schedules%20is%20a%20key%20tool%20for%20recruiting%20and%20retaining%20workers%20in%20both%20the%20public%20and%20private%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelley%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErwin%20told%20BI%20the%20mandate%20suggested%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20about%20how%20the%20federal%20government%20works%20and%20that%C2%A0%26quot%3Bthere's%20this%20myth%20that%20federal%20workers%20aren't%20coming%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20August%20report%20from%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20found%20that%20about%2010%25%20of%20civilian%20workers%20across%20two%20dozen%20agencies%20worked%20remotely%20without%20expectations%20that%20they%20would%20regularly%20work%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErwin%20said%20comments%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20including%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-inauguration-first-steps-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20misrepresented%20the%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20he%20knows%20the%20first%20thing%20about%20the%20federal%20workforce%2C%20who%20they%20are%2C%20where%20they%20are%2C%20and%20the%20valuable%20services%20that%20they%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Musk%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20making%20everybody%20sound%20like%20some%20innovation-blocking%20bureaucrat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErwin%20said%20most%20federal%20employees%20are%20not%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20are%20nationwide.%20Less%20than%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce%20in%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20database%20lives%20in%20DC%20or%20the%20nearby%20states%20of%20Maryland%20and%20Virginia%2C%20a%20recent%20Pew%20analysis%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelley%20also%20said%20lawmakers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-department-government-efficiency-creation-elon-musk-executive-order-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20transition%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3Bspent%20months%20exaggerating%20the%20number%20of%20federal%20employees%20who%20telework%20and%20accusing%20those%20who%20do%20of%20failing%20to%20perform%20the%20duties%20of%20their%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20that%20less%20than%20half%20of%20all%20federal%20jobs%20are%20eligible%20for%20telework%2C%20and%20the%20workers%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20telework%20still%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20work%20hours%20at%20their%20regular%20duty%20stations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%C2%A0Erwin%20and%20Kelley%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-hybrid-work-from-home-jobs-persisting-fewer-new-roles-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etelework%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20also%20essential%20to%20ensuring%20the%20federal%20government's%20continued%20smooth%20operation%20in%20a%20state%20of%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErwin%20said%20that%20after%20September%2011%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20telework%20was%20considered%20essential%20for%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20very%20recently%20that%20telework%20has%20been%20frowned%20upon%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20showed%20how%20the%20ability%20to%20telework%20enabled%20the%20government%20to%20continue%20operating%20relatively%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelley%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-hybrid-jobs-rto-jpmorgan-amazon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20critical%20tool%20for%20federal%20agencies%20to%20maintain%20continuity%20of%20operations%20in%20emergencies%2C%20increase%20disaster%20preparedness%2C%20and%20improve%20efficiency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20hybrid%20work%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20that%20many%20agencies%20have%20consolidated%20or%20sold%20off%20office%20space%20that's%20expensive%20to%20maintain%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3Bmeaning%20there%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20enough%20office%20space%20to%20accommodate%20an%20influx%20of%20on-site%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20federal%20employees%20who%20are%20union%20members%20have%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements%20that%20explicitly%20allow%20for%20remote%20or%20hybrid%20work.%20Erwin%20said%20an%20executive%20order%20would%20not%20override%20those%20agreements%2C%20at%20least%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErwin%20said%20the%20return-to-office%20mandate%20showed%20the%20%26quot%3Bproblem%20with%20governing%20by%20completely%20political%2C%20manufactured%20talking%20points.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20force%20people%20back%20into%20the%20office%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20make%20people%20more%20productive%20for%20the%20American%20taxpayer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A