Fa%3E%2C%20its%20eye-catching%20visual%20style%2C%20or%20the%20acclaimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguy-pearce-movie-roles-memento-the-brutalist-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperformances%3C%2Fa%3E%20propelling%20it%20to%20awards%20season%20glory.%20It's%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsora-ai-film-movies-openai-who-uses-special-effects-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20film's%20use%20of%20it%20should%20make%20it%20less%20deserving%20of%20artistic%20praise%20and%20potential%20awards.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20reached%20a%20peak%20this%20weekend%20after%20excerpts%20from%20an%20interview%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Brutalist%26quot%3B%20editor%20D%C3%A1vid%20Jancs%C3%B3%20went%20viral%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJancs%C3%B3%20told%20online%20tech%20magazine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redsharknews.com%2Fwhy-epic-period-drama-movie-the-brutalist-was-shot-on-vistavision%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERed%20Shark%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20production%20team%20used%20AI%20to%20perfect%20minute%20pronunciation%20details%20in%20the%20Hungarian%20accents%20of%20stars%20Adrien%20Brody%20and%20Felicity%20Jones%2C%20who%20play%20Hungarian%20Jews%20who%20flee%20Europe%20after%20World%20War%20II%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20life%20in%20America.%20(The%20film%20includes%20scenes%20in%20both%20Hungarian%20and%20English.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJancs%C3%B3%2C%20who%20is%20a%20native%20Hungarian%20speaker%20himself%2C%20said%20the%20language%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20learn%20to%20pronounce.%20So%20while%20Brody%20and%20Jones%20had%20dialect%20coaching%20and%20did%20a%20%26quot%3Bfabulous%20job%26quot%3B%20learning%20the%20language%2C%20the%20filmmakers%20wanted%20to%20perfect%20the%20dialogue%20%26quot%3Bso%20that%20not%20even%20locals%20will%20spot%20any%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c6ae45e-2f87-4507-b083-5cec9d93e201%5C%22%3E'The%20Brutalist'%20used%20AI%20to%20improve%20Adrien%20Brody's%20accent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJancs%C3%B3%20said%20they%20first%20tried%20to%20use%20ADR%20(automated%20dialogue%20replacement)%20in%20post-production%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20work.%20So%20the%20team%20opted%20to%20feed%20Brody%20and%20Jones'%20voices%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-earl-jones-paid-only-7000-to-voice-darth-vader-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERespeecher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20software%20company%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20let%20one%20person%20speak%20in%20the%20voice%20of%20another%2C%20then%20fed%20in%20Jancs%C3%B3's%20own%20voice%20to%20finesse%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20very%20careful%20about%20keeping%20their%20performances.%20It's%20mainly%20just%20replacing%20letters%20here%20and%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%20Jancs%C3%B3%20added%20that%20generative%20AI%20was%20used%20to%20craft%20the%20final%20sequence%20where%20viewers%20see%20architectural%20drawings%20and%20completed%20buildings%20in%20the%20style%20of%20Adrien%20Brody's%20fictional%20architect%20L%C3%A1szl%C3%B3%20T%C3%B3th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20editor%20said%20that%20he%20knew%20it%20was%20controversial%20to%20talk%20about%20using%20AI%20in%20film%2C%20but%20maintained%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20nothing%20in%20the%20film%20using%20AI%20that%20hasn't%20been%20done%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20makes%20the%20process%20a%20lot%20faster.%20We%20use%20AI%20to%20create%20these%20tiny%20little%20details%20that%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20or%20the%20time%20to%20shoot%2C%26quot%3B%20Jancs%C3%B3%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232ac1d0f-3a84-4587-98bf-aa7babf8be99%5C%22%3ESome%20fans%20are%20turning%20on%20'The%20Brutalist%2C'%20but%20the%20news%20won't%20impact%20Oscar%20nominations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%2C%20which%20comes%20days%20before%20Thursday's%20Oscar%20nominations%20announcement%2C%20threw%20social%20media%20into%20a%20frenzy%2C%20with%20many%20film%20fans%20criticizing%20the%20movie's%20use%20of%20AI.%20Some%20have%20even%20suggested%20the%20movie%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmidsommarz%2Fstatus%2F1881027245290229919%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eor%20Brody%3C%2Fa%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmoonyswonka%2Fstatus%2F1880764559537147989%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20be%20disqualified%20over%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%20four-hour%20epic%20has%20been%20a%20sensation%20since%20premiering%20at%20the%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20in%20September%2C%20where%20director%20Brady%20Corbet%20won%20the%20festival's%20Silver%20Lion%20award.%20In%20the%20months%20since%2C%20it's%20continued%20to%20rack%20up%20more%20wins%2C%20most%20recently%20taking%20home%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolden-globes-behind-the-scenes-candid-photos-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolden%20Globes%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20best%20director%20for%20Corbet%2C%20best%20actor%20in%20a%20drama%20for%20Brody%2C%20and%20best%20motion%20picture%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20on%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FN4SHTONS%2Fstatus%2F1881012738182496403%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoked%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Brutalist%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20latest%20best%20picture%20contender%20to%20be%20knocked%20out%20of%20the%20race%20after%20%26quot%3BAnora%26quot%3B%20faced%20backlash%20for%20not%20using%20an%20intimacy%20coordinator%2C%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20papal%20thriller%20%26quot%3BConclave%26quot%3B%20to%20win.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20Ralph%20Fiennes%20drama%20does%20clinch%20a%20nomination%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Brutalist%26quot%3B%20doesn't%2C%20it%20likely%20won't%20be%20due%20to%20the%20latter's%20use%20of%20AI%3A%20Oscar%20