20is%20not%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jhili%20was%20able%20to%20monitor%20her%20second%20pregnancy%20closely%20without%20the%20financial%20strain.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20Ganjam%20District%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20she%20was%20offered%20up%20to%20three%20ultrasound%20scans%20for%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ASHA%20worker%20informing%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20about%20the%20free%20ultrasound%20services%20launched%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398459%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20ASHA%20worker%20informing%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20about%20the%20free%20ultrasound%20services%20launched%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20ASHA%20%5BAccredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist%5D%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3Etold%20me%20that%20it%20is%20for%20free%2C%20I%20did%20not%20believe%20her%20at%20first.%20But%20when%20I%20went%20to%20the%20centre%2C%20no%20money%20was%20taken%20from%20me.%20It%20came%20as%20a%20relief.%20I%20underwent%20three%20scans%20in%20my%20third%2C%20seventh%2C%20and%20ninth%20months%20of%20pregnancy.%20I%20was%20very%20worried%20about%20my%20child%20but%20the%20doctor%20told%20me%20everything%20was%20fine%3B%20my%20baby%20was%20healthy%20and%20it%20was%20positioned%20normally%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jhili.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20thing%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20ensure%20was%20that%20I%20keep%20on%20taking%20iron-rich%20food%2C%20such%20as%20jaggery%20and%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20and%20iron%20tablets.%20My%20haemoglobin%20was%2010%20%5Bnormal%20range%20is%2012.0-15.5%20g%2FdL%5D.%20I%20followed%20all%20the%20instructions%20and%20my%20baby%20was%20born%20a%20month%20back.%20Both%20of%20us%20are%20healthy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20diagnostic%20services%20to%20underserved%20populations%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20Parida%20IAS%20spearheaded%20the%20Nirikhyana%20initiative%20in%20Ganjam%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20glaring%20gap%20in%20access%20to%20essential%20diagnostic%20services%2C%20especially%20ultrasounds%20for%20pregnant%20women%2C%20in%20r